task.procedures:
- Use openpyxl.styles Bold class to weighten the header title;
- All colors for rows should be opaque-colored (low opacity);
- The header row should be frozen and have a "cold" color (low value in R for the color spectrum);
- Borders horizontal Sides should be opaque to the point they're almost transparent;
- Borders vertical Sides should be opaque grey, EXCEPT for the header rows, which should be deep grey to black;
